{"tid":1663482,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"自認是香港人嘅入一入嚟！今晚你地有個任務！","createTime":"2019-10-19T12:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T12:58:11.000Z","uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef976ee6b0228769768910adbfbebd9bc456318","tid":1663482,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:17:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">說服你地身邊冇不反就唔撚出嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地香港人嘅兄弟姊妹被人斬,被人姦, 被人殺！<br />\n<br />\n你地都唔撚企出嚟, 你地有咩資格繼續自認是<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[black]<span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人</span>[/black]</span></strong>啊！<br />\n<br />\n聽日如果有一百萬人上街, 我洗鬼同個政府打餐死！<br />\n<br />\n人權法輕鬆就通過, 反對嘅參議員將會被美國反共民意吞噬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我預計聽日應該谷到幾十萬人出來遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是唔夠啊！唔夠啊！唔撚夠啊！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n我求下你地向身邊曾經出過去參加合法遊行嘅朋友進行道德要脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一位手足拖兩位終極和理非一齊去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個Post必須上熱門, 一個深黃叫多兩個淺黃/中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />輕鬆過百萬人行街街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b438e6b9bbfaec20312a6a32a43b957d06454d","tid":1663482,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:18:27.000Z","msg":"大埔手足當街被劏！要令國際知道！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1663444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1663444</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">幫手用twitter retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n向國際講港人響遊行前遭襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的就係要令港人噤聲!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"6669feec709f1c134b38c2db8fef528061edbce5","tid":1663482,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:18:27.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f160b977f83da0cd1a62aeb47b3182d95e1f26c","tid":1663482,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"屌 錯排版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84a45f600684bd4e1776688f43e926870727b3d","tid":1663482,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"照推爆佢啊！<br />\n無論你是勇武定和理非 我要一百萬人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3851e67a2e1520460ed122b0254787d3d3549e45","tid":1663482,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"聽日上街嘅先配 香港人之名！"},{"pid":"ad47475839b7bb5fabe3fd91a9bd9a63e7d29239","tid":1663482,"uid":328969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e598df44cd82528b18b7217bba778a3c27a35d91","tid":1663482,"uid":294916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:24:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a19f23afa27b6da9acb28fd238c45bcfab70c886","tid":1663482,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"我叫左啦 你地呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1101f987a93f1698da83d22d2cb0b2fbb7ebcaf6","tid":1663482,"uid":294916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-